{"type":null,"faqId":33725,"title":"备忘录中如何新建地理闹钟提醒？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">桌面-备忘录-新建备忘录-地理闹钟 -指定位置-选择位置后保存即可。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">关于地理位置的选择，可以通过两种方式，一种是输入关键字，通过选定查询后的某一兴趣点指定，一种是直接通过手指长按地图选定指定地点。在设定地点时，需要网络。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">由于该提醒是基于位置的提醒，需要GPS开启，该提醒才会生效。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":139,"faqType":"应用程序管理","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8445","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Application-Management","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748703000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":12,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"新建,地理围栏,位置提醒","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}